Class MyAdapterSearch

  • java.lang.Object
    • android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<MyViewHolderSearch>
      • ultramirinc.champs_mood.fragments.MyAdapterSearch

  • public class MyAdapterSearch
extends android.support.v7.widget.RecyclerView.Adapter<MyViewHolderSearch>
    Created by William on 2017-04-06. This class creates a binding between the raw data and the visual interpretation for the results . This class binds it with a MyViewHolderNotification object.
